          <p style="line-height: 150%" align="center"><b><font color="#FFFFFF"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:隶书;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;</span><font face="宋体"><span style="mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman"><font size="3">时间：2005年7月30-31日（星期六、日）</font></span><span style="font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></font></font></b></p>
